{"tid":1830241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不服來辯，最新藍店：燈塔 （附多link多證據同欣師）","createTime":"2020-01-19T12:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T11:23:52.000Z","uid":305822,"like":95,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"15f18962a2c77fb61f1636fac455a5b6fd86d3ff","tid":1830241,"uid":305822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T12:29:43.000Z","msg":"唔該睇曬所有link<br />\n大家一直都無視咗燈塔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我發現到一個漏洞！大家遺忘咗六月娘！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1673817\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1673817</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n遵理員工遣責暴徒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1322455\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1322455</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n燈塔老闆六月娘貴為警察榮譽會長，撐警撐到奶鞋底咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前明明po過相 六月之後就del曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KtvTmt9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKtvTmt9.png&h=4c2bb935&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家知唔知點解遵理幾年前比奧斯卡馬件事搞到上唔到市 ，六月娘都好似唔care？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為條友一早就已經返蝗國搞緊補習同教育，再幫d人落香港考試，做新香港人，大家見到班細路住新界講野歪歪地，有一部分都關佢事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣做同每日150冇咩分別，反而仲恐怖。每日150有好多中年/廢老，過幾年就瓜柴，但係佢送班蝗落黎係搶大家資源同學位，都係製造緊會票投民建聯嘅年輕一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要記得，佢手頭上係有極大量呢幾屆應屆dse考生嘅資料，點解拉人可以拉得咁快？咁大個data base .... <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講係講到咁多，歡迎補充。學生們，其實燈塔真係垃圾黎，出面大把中小型勁好多。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（旗下有老師係黃就真嘅，不過同好多公務員係黃嘅一樣道理囉，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過提提大家，大家最愛嘅欣師都係偽黃牆頭草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n[達哥2.0]yylam始終唔肯屌警+藍扮黃事件[多圖]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/nhtRyHX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/nhtRyHX</a><br />\n#385 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n大家係有叫過光復香港，係有骨氣就咪撚再補，又話時代革命，又要一車車去補藍到發紅嘅店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出面大把好老師，問下身邊同學，再唔係ig開個po問，毒撚就上校園台問人有咩推薦。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我祝繼續補燈塔嘅你中文攞2，去做毅進仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"4c4d31a8aa9d199f7aed0a751e7b69389a183501","tid":1830241,"uid":305822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T12:36:53.000Z","msg":"補充<br />\nyy講要還黑警公道 俾黃色經濟圈收左佢皮開始多空位<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1828255\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1828255</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"88b28f549edf51f97e00342f320a7887c47e3f7c","tid":1830241,"uid":79059,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T12:50:04.000Z","msg":"中學手足做嘢啦"},{"pid":"d3fe9600d8e8be12d3e298ff3a0e271fbc5c7420","tid":1830241,"uid":191926,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T12:53:51.000Z","msg":"小心六月娘告你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n要記得，佢手頭上係有極大量呢幾屆應屆dse考生嘅資料，點解拉人可以拉得咁快？咁大個data base ...."},{"pid":"dd7cc9bb594a2910dee48293f97c520152dbaa2d","tid":1830241,"uid":322622,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T13:07:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"adb781fe0f42b8869d82e5f8f2b2da541a680c42","tid":1830241,"uid":319616,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dd7cc9bb594a2910dee48293f97c520152dbaa2d","tid":1830241,"uid":322622,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-